Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.05,0:02:31.44,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}散发异样的情感 让我厌恶
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.56,0:02:36.83,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H42&}你总是找着悲伤借口
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.83,0:02:40.23,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&H42&}扮演着女主角 让我憎恨
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.45,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5\3a&H7E&}泪水根本不适合你吧
