Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.68,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}说出告别
Comment: 1,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.49,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Slash your tears away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.94,0:03:39.24,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我不会再逃避
